{"pageContext":{"notebook":"AWS","section":"AWS EC2","page":{"id":"0-a7ba2927f2a7d14c9f4c027305437dfe!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2011","self":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/pages/0-a7ba2927f2a7d14c9f4c027305437dfe!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2011","createdTime":"2017-08-28T16:08:13.106Z","title":"EC2 Linux에 node.js , npm 설치","createdByAppId":"","links":{"oneNoteEmbedUrl":{"href":"https://onedrive.live.com/redir.aspx?cid=bc575ab8e2ab9833&page=edit&resid=BC575AB8E2AB9833!2000&parId=BC575AB8E2AB9833!109&wd=target%28AWS%20EC2.one%7Ca9db5ec1-48b3-a24e-bc07-98d85a74ce00%2FEC2%20Linux%EC%97%90%20node.js%20%2C%20npm%20%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%7Cb02ac177-a957-054e-9c13-bb2a519957b8%2F%29"},"oneNoteClientUrl":{"href":"onenote:https://d.docs.live.net/bc575ab8e2ab9833/Documents/AWS/AWS%20EC2.one#EC2%20Linux%EC%97%90%20node.js%20%2C%20npm%20%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98&section-id=a9db5ec1-48b3-a24e-bc07-98d85a74ce00&page-id=b02ac177-a957-054e-9c13-bb2a519957b8&end"},"oneNoteWebUrl":{"href":"https://onedrive.live.com/redir.aspx?cid=bc575ab8e2ab9833&page=edit&resid=BC575AB8E2AB9833!2000&parId=BC575AB8E2AB9833!109&wd=target%28AWS%20EC2.one%7Ca9db5ec1-48b3-a24e-bc07-98d85a74ce00%2FEC2%20Linux%EC%97%90%20node.js%20%2C%20npm%20%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98%7Cb02ac177-a957-054e-9c13-bb2a519957b8%2F%29"}},"contentUrl":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/pages/0-a7ba2927f2a7d14c9f4c027305437dfe!1-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2011/content","lastModifiedTime":"2017-11-01T11:06:17Z","parentSection@odata.context":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/$metadata#me/notes/sections('0-BC575AB8E2AB9833%212011')/pages('0-a7ba2927f2a7d14c9f4c027305437dfe%211-BC575AB8E2AB9833%212011')/parentSection(id,name,self)/$entity","parentSection":{"id":"0-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2011","name":"AWS EC2","self":"https://www.onenote.com/api/v1.0/me/notes/sections/0-BC575AB8E2AB9833!2011"},"content":"       EC2 Linux AMI에서 node.js , npm설치하기    요약         nvm설치     nvm 명령어로 node 설치. (개인적으론 공홈의 LTS버전인 v6.11.2설치함)￼그럼 자동으로 npm 도 따라서 설치됨.     npm명령어로 pm2 설치가능.     그런데 이 설치버전은 ec2-user폴더 안에서만 작동됨.            Latest Version     https://nodejs.org/ko/download/package-manager/        Npmjs.com에서 pm2자료를 찾다가 발견한 링크    https://keymetrics.io/2015/02/03/installing-node-js-and-io-js-with-nvm/        2012년 개인블로그    http://iconof.com/blog/how-to-install-setup-node-js-on-amazon-aws-ec2-complete-guide/    node.js공식 GitHub    https://github.com/nodejs/node/blob/master/BUILDING.md    아마존 공식문서 ( 이 방법으로 설치함 )    http://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/sdk-for-javascript/v2/developer-guide/setting-up-node-on-ec2-instance.html        2017년 개인블로그    https://github.com/npm/npm/issues/17996 에서 얻은 링크.    https://sharpten.com/blog/2017/01/24/setting-node-js-amazon-ec2-instance.html           ","html":"\n\t\t<div style=\"position:absolute;left:48px;top:139px;width:576px\">\n\t\t\t<h1 style=\"font-size:16pt;color:#1e4e79;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">EC2 Linux AMI&#xC5D0;&#xC11C; node.js , npm&#xC124;&#xCE58;&#xD558;&#xAE30;</h1>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">&#xC694;&#xC57D;</p>\n\t\t\t<ol>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span lang=\"en-US\">nvm<span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC124;&#xCE58;</span></span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span lang=\"en-US\">nvm <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xBA85;&#xB839;&#xC5B4;&#xB85C;</span> node <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC124;&#xCE58;</span>. (<span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xAC1C;&#xC778;&#xC801;&#xC73C;&#xB860;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xACF5;&#xD648;&#xC758;</span> LTS<span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xBC84;&#xC804;&#xC778;</span> v6.11.2<span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC124;&#xCE58;&#xD568;</span>)&#xFFFC;<span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xADF8;&#xB7FC;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC790;&#xB3D9;&#xC73C;&#xB85C;</span> npm <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xB3C4;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xB530;&#xB77C;&#xC11C;</span> <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC124;&#xCE58;&#xB428;</span>.</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><span lang=\"en-US\">npm<span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xBA85;&#xB839;&#xC5B4;&#xB85C;</span> pm2 <span lang=\"ko-KR\">&#xC124;&#xCE58;&#xAC00;&#xB2A5;</span>.</span></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>&#xADF8;&#xB7F0;&#xB370;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xC774;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xC124;&#xCE58;&#xBC84;&#xC804;&#xC740;<span lang=\"en-US\"> ec2-user</span>&#xD3F4;&#xB354;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xC548;&#xC5D0;&#xC11C;&#xB9CC;<span lang=\"en-US\"> </span>&#xC791;&#xB3D9;&#xB428;<span lang=\"en-US\">.</span></li>\n\t\t\t</ol>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<h2 lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">Latest Version </h2>\n\t\t\t<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/ko/download/package-manager/\">https://nodejs.org/ko/download/package-manager/</a></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<h2 lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">Npmjs.com&#xC5D0;&#xC11C; pm2&#xC790;&#xB8CC;&#xB97C; &#xCC3E;&#xB2E4;&#xAC00; &#xBC1C;&#xACAC;&#xD55C; &#xB9C1;&#xD06C;</h2>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><a href=\"https://keymetrics.io/2015/02/03/installing-node-js-and-io-js-with-nvm/\">https://keymetrics.io/2015/02/03/installing-node-js-and-io-js-with-nvm/</a></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<h2 style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">2012&#xB144; &#xAC1C;&#xC778;&#xBE14;&#xB85C;&#xADF8;</h2>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><a href=\"http://iconof.com/blog/how-to-install-setup-node-js-on-amazon-aws-ec2-complete-guide/\" style=\"font-family:Helvetica Neue;font-size:9pt\">http://iconof.com/blog/how-to-install-setup-node-js-on-amazon-aws-ec2-complete-guide/</a></p>\n\t\t\t<h2 style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">node.js&#xACF5;&#xC2DD; GitHub</h2>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><a href=\"https://github.com/nodejs/node/blob/master/BUILDING.md\" style=\"font-family:Helvetica Neue;font-size:9pt\">https://github.com/nodejs/node/blob/master/BUILDING.md</a></p>\n\t\t\t<h2 style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">&#xC544;&#xB9C8;&#xC874; &#xACF5;&#xC2DD;&#xBB38;&#xC11C;<span lang=\"en-US\"> ( </span><span lang=\"en-US\">&#xC774; &#xBC29;&#xBC95;&#xC73C;&#xB85C; &#xC124;&#xCE58;&#xD568;</span><span lang=\"en-US\"> )</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><a href=\"http://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/sdk-for-javascript/v2/developer-guide/setting-up-node-on-ec2-instance.html\" style=\"font-family:Helvetica Neue;font-size:9pt\">http://docs.aws.amazon.com/ko_kr/sdk-for-javascript/v2/developer-guide/setting-up-node-on-ec2-instance.html</a></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t\t<h2 lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-size:14pt;color:#2e75b5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">2017&#xB144; &#xAC1C;&#xC778;&#xBE14;&#xB85C;&#xADF8;</h2>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><a href=\"https://github.com/npm/npm/issues/17996\">https://github.com/npm/npm/issues/17996</a> &#xC5D0;&#xC11C; &#xC5BB;&#xC740; &#xB9C1;&#xD06C;<span lang=\"en-US\">.</span></p>\n\t\t\t<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><a href=\"https://sharpten.com/blog/2017/01/24/setting-node-js-amazon-ec2-instance.html\">https://sharpten.com/blog/2017/01/24/setting-node-js-amazon-ec2-instance.html</a></p>\n\t\t\t<br>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\n\n"}}}